
MVP
User friendly page (page 1) where visitors can enter a need.
Submitted need will renter onto a needs page (page 2).
User can respond to need by checking the boxes they want and then submitting (page 2).
Once the counter is reached on the checked/submitted item, that need is removed (page 2).
  - the needer receives an email alert
  - the needer and offerer connect on their own
  
Stretch
Dropdown on needs page (page 1) to categorize the need.
Categorization on the needs summary page (page 2) that breaks the needs into categories.
Submit counter and erasing items
